    "text": "This key displays a warning message indicating that the user is approaching the quota limit for a product. It appears in the UI, likely as a notification or alert, to inform the user about the impending limit and potentially prevent unexpected disruptions. The `productName` variable will be dynamically replaced with the name of the product.",
